title: Railworks TS2015 AP Class 86/87 Sound Pack (Pro)
description:
As requested, updated sound pack. Class 87 cab light fix 27.08.2014.

During the installation process, these sounds will be applied to the InterCity Executive liveried class 86 included with the WCML North route, the BR Blue liveried class 87 included with the WCML over Shap route, the Class 86 Add-on & the BR Class 87 Add-on.



Please support the developers and buy some of their content if you can afford it.


If you would like to contribute, please read the Readme.pdf.
